Package org.infinispan.extendedstats.logging

Interface Log

All Superinterfaces:
org.jboss.logging.BasicLogger
@MessageLogger(projectCode="ISPN") public interface Log extends org.jboss.logging.BasicLogger
The JBoss Logging interface which defined the logging methods for the extended statistics module. The id range for this is 25001-26000
Since:
6.0
Author:
Pedro Ruivo
